Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good  morning  everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么美妙的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这不才四点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The  early  bird  catches  the  worm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们身负喜翠庄的日常业务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着还要准备我们的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了完成这繁重的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能从削减年轻人的睡眠时间开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  接下来要和anything开一场会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发去员工食堂  Here  we  go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊  崇子小姐突然好有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good  moring  Miss巴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始这美妙的一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来  Miss巴请就座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来开始会议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要拿出干劲来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are  you  ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  芥川龙之介写这部「罗生门」的经过是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时芥川和他的青梅竹马  吉田弥生的婚约告吹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它很少会响的所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  男朋友怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要说男女朋友什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么呀  真难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在上课的时候打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得你是不是一直都在干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是个女高中生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我收到了张请帖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘他要结婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定会参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  工作很忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  各种原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贺电的话我会发一个的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来缘结婚了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被他超前了呢  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  妈妈你一直在换男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟别人交往到底是种什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？  你又把上其他男人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准还对你爸爸单相思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单相思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算什么口气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家还以为说了一句不错的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是单相思这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本想不到会从放荡的妈妈嘴里说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为忘不了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才摸索其他恋情的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让这份感情又得不到回报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那人去世至今也有十五年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我会开始这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也没有必要得到回报了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少能遇到让自己喜欢到这种地步的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是遇到  就已经足够幸运了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然为妈妈的单相思心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  单相思…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么我会想要放弃阿孝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连小民都能那么认真地对彻先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会想不到这是单相思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧  完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一个外行而言做得挺不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是试穿  再做做微调了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名同学穿穿看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种说法是穿上婚纱婚期就会延后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我穿的话  下摆肯定要拖地的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉之前貌似也有过一次这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种怪讨厌的既视感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已  已经可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴小姐正在努力地做我们那份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让鹤来同学穿穿看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那边没准还不如崇子小姐有料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没胸反而方便试穿不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之没胸走遍天下都不怕  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你就要开始试做宴会料理了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我基本上都有点底了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过用不着帮忙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  我已经放弃胡萝卜政策了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有严苛的环境  人是无法摆脱低潮的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于想通了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要像当时冷酷无情的莲先生那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷酷…无情？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民好迟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是大家一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后的调整还…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种轻飘飘的衣服我绝对不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是…小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  小民！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我不爽这没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那件婚纱是我和小菜还有结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了少爷和崇子小姐才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做得非常用心！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却把那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你非常用心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道彻先生就不是了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你践踏了非常用心的彻先生的心意！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻  彻先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要单恋阿孝！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小民这样直接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:08:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少给我去搞什么单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去跟彻先生交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死  去死  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  要是死了就没法交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我已经决定要单恋阿孝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝什么的那种傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民你又没见过他！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟彻先生相比  男人全都是傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}小民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生他那么有型！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那么出色！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再吵了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民  等一等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘛…那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实对绪花有点意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…真是有点喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是说我就要怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看到她时会有些兴奋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会去猜测她接下来又会做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看到你时我会放不下心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我刚说了什么过分的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:10:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算彻先生并不喜欢我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一样会关注我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  基本都弄干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我还没谈过恋爱什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得这一定很美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一直单相思下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然吵架是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得绪花和小民都很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像那样思念着一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被你们感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么感动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  试着拿些白色鲜花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来有在电视上看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会显得华贵一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把楼梯旁边的花拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的必须要和彻先生交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想和彻先生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是这个不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要交往  所以会继续单相思的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直冲目标  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花…又吵架…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋复活祭哟～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后  婚礼的准备也顺利进行着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中我下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼顺利结束后就去告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无微不至
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  多亏了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼一定会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民  这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是女人一生中最漂亮的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人一生中…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛花团的时候一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学毕业后好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候和崇子好上的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们就此成为夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能向大家宣布这件事情我非常感动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大家面前发誓   从今天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们夫妻将互相帮助  互相分享
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营造一个幸福的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开场结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是和时间赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司仪什么的  好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  押水同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名的头发没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪  待会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中的押水同学  真新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房如战场  开工了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻  发号施令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你是这里的主厨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那里的蔬菜处理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把鲤鱼的鳞片刮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有把天妇罗油炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后把黄瓜雕花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真过分啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此由我诵读一下贺电
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新郎的姐姐  松前皋月发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说雨后土固
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}注：形容经历挫折之后现状会变得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不知今天天气如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之坚固是件好事  缘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对男人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一道料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就是最后一道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请柬？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场婚礼  我们也被邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都好美味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还是第一次好好品尝彻先生的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我没能阻止…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  下一个节目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的命中注定的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的  崇子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那边在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  爱的Baiser
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}注：Baiser  法语  接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  有反应就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的婚礼  我完全没有插手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  这里的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及喜翠庄工作的年轻人们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举办了如此成功的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提下我的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40年前  我和已逝的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有在这里的电六
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  和电六先生三人一起建起了喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕受挫  迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会毫不畏惧挑战未知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造新的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位以及大家一起创造的新的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就满怀期待  在远处喝着粗茶守望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守望？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利…结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快收拾完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.95,0:22:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才老板娘所说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家都聚在这里不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前电六先生和我谈过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电六先生他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40年间不曾间断记录着的工作日记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该让谁来继承了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷  就是说要离开喜翠庄了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  豆丁老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份工作日记就是喜翠庄的历史本身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪和欢笑全都记录于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.43,0:23:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得如此破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄将在这次的雪洞祭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.81,0:23:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与日记一同结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}要去见他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}单相思的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐心的等待也是男人的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花 你才不是什么没味的咖啡
